description:
The 61st General Conference Session is unparalleled to any GC Session in the history of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. It is the first time ever that the details of the Session are being broadcast in every social media channel of the Church in FOUR different languages. ANN has an exclusive interview with Communication Department Director, Williams Costa Jr, to discover more about this comprehensive communication strategy and the department’s future plans. We also go behind-the-scenes to find out what attendees do during their times of leisure at the Session. 

Tune in to this episode of ANN for these exclusive segments, mission reports, and to hear more about what went on during the third day of business at the 61st General Conference Session of Seventh-day Adventists.

ANN Website: https://adventist.news/
ANN Twitter: https://twitter.com/adventistnews
